<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a12Feb1939"><font color="red">12 February 1939</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Richard de la Mere): I am enclosing the title-page with the indication of the changes Mr Joyce would like you to make. I hope that they are not impossible either technically or from the point of bibliophily &hellip; send advance copies abroad &hellip; unbound but containing the full text &hellip; Mr Gillet. </div>
